longBusinessSummary: Initiator Pharma A/S, a clinical stage life science company, develops drugs targeting unmet medical needs within the central and peripheral nervous system. Its product pipeline includes Pudafensine, a monoamine reuptake inhibitor primarily targeting the dopamine system for both treatment resistant organic erectile dysfunction and neuropathic pain in Phase 2b clinical trials; IP2018, a monoamine reuptake inhibitor completed Phase 2a for the treatment of psychogenic erectile dysfunction; and IP2016, which is in preclinical development for the treatment of depression and pain. Initiator Pharma A/S was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Copenhagen, Denmark.
